body_html:
Around Oct 21, a change was made so that the format of ops_to_register.h is
slightly different, but the print_selective_... tool should be in sync with
that.

Also, an "ops missing error" would seem more likely to happen when running
than during compilation.

  • What is the error that bazel prints at this point?
  • Can you share the generated ops_to_register.h?
